<item>
            <title>[SOLR-146] Solr::Response::Base.make_response raises misleading exception when response class exists but raises an exception on creation</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-146</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When attempting to instantiate Solr::Response::InsertRequestTypeHere, Solr::Response::Base.make_response rescues all exceptions. If an existing Solr::Response class has an error on instantiation, an &quot;unknown request type&quot; error is raised, which is misleading.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
